snippet.title: Cereus Game Trailer - Get Updates: http://aesth.games/
snippet.description:
http://aesth.games/

A STRATEGIC TOWER DEFENSE MOBILE GAME. MINUS THE TOWERS.

Defend your base to test not only your reflexes, but decision-making skills.

DEFEND your base. 

TAP enemies.

SWIPE to create barriers.

DROP bombs.

ABSORB cells from fallen enemies to EVOLVE your abilities.

TAKE ON increasingly challenging Enemies and Bosses.
